Michelle Berube https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Berube 0 Michelle Berube is an American actress and magician assistant, and retired Olympic gymnast. She is most notable for her role as one of the Masked Magician's assistants from Breaking the Magician's Code: Magic's Biggest Secrets Finally Revealed.
